Pass -j<N> on the make command line for GNU Make 3.x compatibility.
GNUMAKEFLAGS is only honored by GNU Make 4.2+; injecting -j on the
command line works on all GNU Make versions. Skip when using nmake.
Shared helper inject_make_parallelism_args() in resource_sets.bzl.
Do not set GNUMAKEFLAGS in env to avoid a no-op on GNU Make 3.x.

